product_name: Keen Marshall Mid WP Hiking Boots - Women's
long_description: With waterproof uppers that keep freet dry and well-cushioned midsoles for continued comfort, the women's Keen Marshall Mid WP hiking boots provide a supportive platform perfect for hiking. Waterproof nylon mesh uppers promote breathability and hold up to light hiking; synthetic leather overlays provide lightweight support. KEEN.DRY(TM) waterproof breathable membranes keep feet dry while allowing perspiration to dissipate. Polyester mesh linings are highly breathable and wick moisture away from the feet for comfort. EVA footbeds provide ample cushioning, and are removable to accommodate orthotics. High-rebound polyurethane midsoles supply shock absorption for all-day comfort. Supportive thermoplastic urethane shanks enhance torsional stability on uneven terrain. Keen Marshall Mid WP hiking boots have nonmarking rubber outsoles with 4mm multidirectional lugs that offer excellent all-around traction.
